I'm lying at your feet here, unloved and nameless; so you should know that I died for liberty -
The world in which I live has been denied to me because there was no place beneath the earth on which they had agreed to hide my body- and not even my mother knew where I'd be;

You came along with flowers, you put them very near, but didn't see how close I lay to these; and as flowers are the tears o'the living it could have meant something had it been otherwise; but all my life people were careless about what happened to me; therefore death found me unnamed.

